files.HelloWorld.cfg:
INIT Init
NEXT Next
INVARIANT Inv
files.HelloWorld.tla:
------------ MODULE HelloWorld -------------

EXTENDS Naturals, FiniteSets, Sequences

VARIABLES
    x,
    y

Init ==
    /\ x = "hello"
    /\ y = 42

Next == 
    /\ x' = IF x = "hello" THEN "world" ELSE "hello"
    /\ y' = 42-y

Inv == 
    ~
    (
        /\ x = "world"
        /\ y = 0
    )
    

===========================================
